<tr><td> </td><td class="diff-context">&nbsp;&nbsp;* What would you do to help mentor students from under-represented minorities and women?</td><td> </td><td class="diff-context">&nbsp;&nbsp;* What would you do to help mentor students from under-represented minorities and women?</td></tr>
